    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/b33b7bc2a3e4b065460cb3abc94432cc.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《King of the Hat》是一款用帽子作为武器的2-4人2D聚会平台游戏！扔出你的帽子攻击，并同时防御并引诱敌人。但要小心！如果有人跳到你的帽子上……就出局！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/4423571d3cefd23311eef6828f71496f.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《King of the Hat》中，你的灵魂就在帽子中，碾碎对手的帽子（和灵魂），以宣示你对他们的统治地位。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/df650790457597dd2ae799ed11a1fe8a.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>帽子扔出后，就会附带火焰且无敌。你可以用它来击败其他玩家，或者抵御对手的同样冒着火焰的帽子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/a7ac6d243b9542b81f1d6de4789ef95d.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>尽管游戏的机制十分易于上手，但《King of the Hat》的玩法也十分有深度，具有高度帽子-竞技性的2人游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.poster.avif?t=1715111749\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.webm?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/9bd0c297a0fa563803f6ddf32d8b3af1.mp4?t=1715111749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>改变规则，添加强化能力，挑战关卡障碍，实现你一直梦想的基于帽子的那些疯狂想法吧。",
